<search>
  <entry>
    <title>JC by paste on luogu</title>
    <url>/JC-by-paste-on-luogu/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><p>在浏览器中，可以使用控制台的 <code>Console</code> 来进行请求。那么，我们能不能利用这一点来快速 JC 别人，甚至隔空 JC 别人呢？答案是，可以的。其实不仅仅是洛谷，其他网站也行，这里只是通过洛谷做一个示范而已。</p>
<h2 id="前置芝士"><a href="#前置芝士" class="headerlink" title="前置芝士"></a>前置芝士</h2><ol>
<li><a href="https://pythonjishu.com/kjvygvaottgnuoy/">JavaScript 之 Fetch 操作</a></li>
<li><a href="https://www.runoob.com/js/js-promise.html">JavaScript 之 Promise</a></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="洛谷的-API"><a href="#洛谷的-API" class="headerlink" title="洛谷的 API"></a>洛谷的 API</h2><p>在洛谷首页，F12打开开发者模式，点“网络”或“NetWork”，然后发一条犇犇，查看请求：</p>
<p><img src="/images/JC-by-paste-on-luogu-1.jpg"></p>
<p><del>显然，</del>postBenben是发犇犇，watching是获取关注的犇犇，点“postBenben”：</p>
<p><img src="/images/JC-by-paste-on-luogu-2.jpg"></p>
<p>然后点”负载“或”Payloads“：</p>
<p><img src="/images/JC-by-paste-on-luogu-3.jpg"></p>
<p>由此可得，发犇犇是对 <a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/feed/postBenben">&#x2F;api&#x2F;feed&#x2F;postBenben</a> 发送一个POST请求，负载只有一条：”content: 犇犇内容“</p>
<p>其他操作也可以用同样的方法抓包，抓包结果：</p>
<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>操作</th>
<th>地址</th>
<th>参数1名称</th>
<th>参数1值</th>
<th>参数2名称</th>
<th>参数2值</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>发犇犇</td>
<td><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/feed/postBenben">&#x2F;api&#x2F;feed&#x2F;postBenben</a></td>
<td>content</td>
<td>犇犇内容</td>
<td>无</td>
<td>无</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>发私信</td>
<td><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/chat/new">&#x2F;api&#x2F;chat&#x2F;new</a></td>
<td>user</td>
<td>接收方uid</td>
<td>content</td>
<td>私信内容</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>修改个签</td>
<td><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateSlogan">&#x2F;api&#x2F;user&#x2F;updateSlogan</a></td>
<td>slogan</td>
<td>新个签</td>
<td>无</td>
<td>无</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>关注&#x2F;取关&#x2F;拉黑</td>
<td><a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateRelationShip">&#x2F;api&#x2F;user&#x2F;updateRelationShip</a></td>
<td>uid</td>
<td>对方uid</td>
<td>relationship</td>
<td>新状态（0&#x3D;取关，1&#x3D;关注，2&#x3D;拉黑）</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<p>备注：先取关才能拉黑</p>
<h2 id="JavaScript，上！"><a href="#JavaScript，上！" class="headerlink" title="JavaScript，上！"></a>JavaScript，上！</h2><p>根据上面分析结果，很容易写出 JavaScript 代码，粘到 Console 中运行即可：</p>
<h4 id="犇犇"><a href="#犇犇" class="headerlink" title="犇犇"></a>犇犇</h4><div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        Benben Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/feed/postBenben&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;犇犇内容&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

    </div>
</div>

<h4 id="私信"><a href="#私信" class="headerlink" title="私信"></a>私信</h4><div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        Chat Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/chat/new&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">user</span>: 对方uid,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;私信内容&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

    </div>
</div>

<h4 id="关注"><a href="#关注" class="headerlink" title="关注"></a>关注</h4><div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        Follow Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateRelationShip&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">uid</span>: 对方uid,</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">relationship</span>: 关系编号（<span class="number">0</span>=取关，<span class="number">1</span>=关注，<span class="number">2</span>=拉黑）</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

    </div>
</div>

<h4 id="个签"><a href="#个签" class="headerlink" title="个签"></a>个签</h4><div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        Slogan Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateSlogan&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">  ],</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">slogan</span>: <span class="string">&quot;新个签&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">&#125;);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

    </div>
</div>

<h2 id="拓展"><a href="#拓展" class="headerlink" title="拓展"></a>拓展</h2><h4 id="第一步"><a href="#第一步" class="headerlink" title="第一步"></a>第一步</h4><p>鉴于 <code>fetch</code> 属于 promise 语法，我们可以用 .then 把他们连接成一条指令，方便执行，例如：</p>
<div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        JavaScript Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight javascript"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;&quot;</span>, &#123;&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">.<span class="title function_">then</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">data</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/feed/postBenben&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;I AK IOI&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">.<span class="title function_">then</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">data</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/chat/new&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">user</span>: -<span class="number">1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">content</span>: <span class="string">&quot;I AK IOI&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">.<span class="title function_">then</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">data</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateSlogan&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">slogan</span>: <span class="string">&quot;I AK IOI&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">.<span class="title function_">then</span>(<span class="function"><span class="params">data</span> =&gt;</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="title function_">fetch</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateRelationShip&quot;</span>, &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">headers</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;content-type&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;application/json&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;referer&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/&quot;</span>],</span><br><span class="line">      [<span class="string">&quot;x-csrf-token&quot;</span>, <span class="variable language_">document</span>.<span class="title function_">querySelector</span>(<span class="string">&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]&quot;</span>).<span class="property">content</span>],</span><br><span class="line">    ],</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">body</span>: <span class="title class_">JSON</span>.<span class="title function_">stringify</span>(&#123;</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">uid</span>: <span class="number">1</span>,</span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">relationship</span>: <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line">    &#125;),</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">method</span>: <span class="string">&quot;POST&quot;</span>,</span><br><span class="line">  &#125;);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;)</span><br><span class="line">;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
    </div>
</div>

<h4 id="下一步"><a href="#下一步" class="headerlink" title="下一步"></a>下一步</h4><p>要是一条指令一条指令手写还是太麻烦了，犹其是当你想恶搞同学的时候，因此我们使用一个 C++ 程序来为我们生成 JavaScript 代码：</p>
<div class='spoiler collapsed'>
    <div class='spoiler-title'>
        C++ Code
    </div>
    <div class='spoiler-content'>
        <figure class="highlight cpp"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#<span class="keyword">include</span><span class="string">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">using</span> <span class="keyword">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> chat[]=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;.then(data =&gt; &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  return fetch(\&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/chat/new\&quot;, &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    headers: [\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;content-type\&quot;, \&quot;application/json\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;referer\&quot;, \&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;x-csrf-token\&quot;, document.querySelector(\&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]\&quot;).content],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    ],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    body: JSON.stringify(&#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      user: %d,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      content: \&quot;%s\&quot;,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    &#125;),\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    method: \&quot;POST\&quot;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  &#125;);\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&#125;)\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> benben[]=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;.then(data =&gt; &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  return fetch(\&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/feed/postBenben\&quot;, &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    headers: [\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;content-type\&quot;, \&quot;application/json\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;referer\&quot;, \&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;x-csrf-token\&quot;, document.querySelector(\&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]\&quot;).content],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    ],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    body: JSON.stringify(&#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      content: \&quot;%s\&quot;,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    &#125;),\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    method: \&quot;POST\&quot;,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  &#125;);\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&#125;)\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> follow[]=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;.then(data =&gt; &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  return fetch(\&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateRelationShip\&quot;, &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    headers: [\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;content-type\&quot;, \&quot;application/json\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;referer\&quot;, \&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;x-csrf-token\&quot;, document.querySelector(\&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]\&quot;).content],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    ],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    body: JSON.stringify(&#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      uid: %d,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      relationship: %d\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    &#125;),\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    method: \&quot;POST\&quot;,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  &#125;);\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&#125;)\n&quot;</span>;<span class="comment">//0=quguan 1=follow 2=lahei</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="type">const</span> <span class="type">char</span> slogan[]=</span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;.then(data =&gt; &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  return fetch(\&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/api/user/updateSlogan\&quot;, &#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    headers: [\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;content-type\&quot;, \&quot;application/json\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;referer\&quot;, \&quot;https://www.luogu.com.cn/\&quot;],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      [\&quot;x-csrf-token\&quot;, document.querySelector(\&quot;meta[name=csrf-token]\&quot;).content],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    ],\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    body: JSON.stringify(&#123;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;      slogan: \&quot;%s\&quot;\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    &#125;),\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;    method: \&quot;POST\&quot;,\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;  &#125;);\n&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;&#125;)\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">string <span class="title">read</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> string&amp; str)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please input &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;str&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;.End with the sentence \&quot;End Of Input\&quot;:\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	string ans,tmp;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="built_in">getline</span>(cin,tmp) &amp;&amp; tmp!=<span class="string">&quot;End Of Input&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">for</span>(<span class="type">char</span> ch:tmp)</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">if</span>(ch==<span class="string">&#x27;\\&#x27;</span>)	ans+=<span class="string">&quot;\\\\&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">else</span>			ans+=ch;</span><br><span class="line">		ans+=<span class="string">&quot;\\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function">string <span class="title">readline</span><span class="params">(<span class="type">const</span> string&amp; str)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please input &quot;</span>&lt;&lt;str&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;:&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	string ans;</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">getline</span>(cin,ans);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">return</span> ans;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="type">int</span> <span class="title">main</span><span class="params">()</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">	string file;</span><br><span class="line">	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Input file name:&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">	cin&gt;&gt;file;</span><br><span class="line">	FILE* fout=<span class="built_in">fopen</span>(file.<span class="built_in">c_str</span>(),<span class="string">&quot;w&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">if</span>(fout==<span class="literal">NULL</span>)	cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Fail.&quot;</span>,<span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">1</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,<span class="string">&quot;fetch(\&quot;\&quot;, &#123;&#125;)\n&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">	<span class="keyword">while</span>(<span class="literal">true</span>)</span><br><span class="line">	&#123;</span><br><span class="line">		cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please select operation type.\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Valid types contain [B]enben [C]hat [F]ollow [S]logan [Q]uit.\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Your selection:_\b&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">char</span> ch;</span><br><span class="line">		cin&gt;&gt;ch;</span><br><span class="line">		cin.<span class="built_in">get</span>();</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="type">int</span> uid,type;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">if</span>(ch&gt;=<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>)	ch=ch-<span class="string">&#x27;a&#x27;</span>+<span class="string">&#x27;A&#x27;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">		<span class="keyword">switch</span>(ch)</span><br><span class="line">		&#123;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;B&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,benben,<span class="built_in">read</span>(<span class="string">&quot;benben content&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>());</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;C&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please input uid of reciever:&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cin&gt;&gt;uid;</span><br><span class="line">				cin.<span class="built_in">get</span>();</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,chat,uid,<span class="built_in">read</span>(<span class="string">&quot;message content&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>());</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;F&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please input uid of the user in the relationship to be updated:&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cin&gt;&gt;uid;</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Please input new relationship\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;0: No relationship\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;1: Follow\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;2: Block\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				cin&gt;&gt;type;</span><br><span class="line">				cin.<span class="built_in">get</span>();</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">if</span>(type==<span class="number">2</span>)	<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,follow,uid,<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,follow,uid,type);</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;S&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,slogan,<span class="built_in">readline</span>(<span class="string">&quot;new slogan&quot;</span>).<span class="built_in">c_str</span>());</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="keyword">break</span>;</span><br><span class="line">			<span class="keyword">case</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Q&#x27;</span>:</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fprintf</span>(fout,<span class="string">&quot;;&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line">				cout&lt;&lt;<span class="string">&quot;Done!\n&quot;</span>;</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">fclose</span>(fout);</span><br><span class="line">				<span class="built_in">exit</span>(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">		&#125;</span><br><span class="line">	&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

